node.text: First of all. I’m picking one person to give $100 to in the comments that tells me how this video touched their heart and shares it on their stories. Second of all, more importantly...don’t let your loyalty become your slavery. Don’t let your “loyalty” be the reason you stay miserable the rest of your life. Be loyal to those that deserve it! Be loyal to those that give you that same type of respect back. TAG someone to this video that needs it! And text me 817.242.2719 if this touched your heart. #trentshelton #loyalty #inspiration

node.text: Who are you going to be? A watcher, a wisher, or a worker?!? Life is way too short NOT to get the most out of your life! You do know you only get one of these, so why not make the most out of it?!? Tag someone to this video who needs it! Text me 817.242.2719 if this was the message your heart needed today.

node.title: Drop a ❤️ if you this message touched your heart

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by T R E N T S H E L T O N on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'When God says he'll give you back better than what you lost, believe him....'.

node.text:
𝘐 𝘯𝘦𝘦𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘵𝘰 𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘬𝘯𝘰𝘸 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴 𝘪𝘴 𝘵𝘳𝘶𝘦. ⁣⁣
⁣
Drop a 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇🏾 with an upgrade 𝐆𝐨𝐝 blessed you with!!! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
•𝐑𝐞𝐡𝐚𝐛 𝐒𝐞𝐬𝐬𝐢𝐨𝐧• ⁣⁣
I need you to understand sometimes you have to lose certain things, so God can bless you with better things. Certain things HAVE TO end so better things can begin. The storm never makes sense until you see the growth it produced. ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Remember, sometimes the best way to add to your life is to subtract from it 🤷🏾‍♂️⁣⁣
⁣⁣
⁣

node.text:
Drop a ❤️ if you believe in hard work! 

Progression is an ugly road that leads to a beautiful place. Plant the seed. Water the seed. Be patient. Reap the harvest. 

This motto is something we instill to our athletes and so much more. 

Live It. Breathe It. Be It.

Drop a ❤️ if you’re not going to waste your life! 

Somebody needs your story….let nothing stop you from giving it to the world.

node.text:
𝘐 𝘯𝘦𝘦𝘥 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘵𝘰 𝘋𝘳𝘰𝘱 𝘢 🙏🏾 𝘐𝘧 𝘺𝘰𝘶 𝘬𝘯𝘰𝘸 𝘵𝘩𝘪𝘴 𝘪𝘴 𝘵𝘳𝘶𝘦. ⁣⁣
⁣
Drop a 𝐜𝐨𝐦𝐦𝐞𝐧𝐭 👇🏾 with an upgrade 𝐆𝐨𝐝 blessed you with!!! ⁣

Sometimes the best way God adds to your life is to subtract from it. Sometimes things have to happen that will immediately hurt your heart, but eventually heal your soul. Faith doesn’t mean it makes sense in the moment, it means that it will work out for the good of your life. 

#faith #god #sundayfunday #sundayvibes #rehabtime #love

node.text:
DROP A ❤️ IF YOU FEEL THIS! ⁣
⁣
HOW DO YOU PROTECT YOUR PEACE? ⁣
⁣
•𝐑𝐄𝐇𝐀𝐁 𝐒𝐄𝐒𝐒𝐈𝐎𝐍•⁣
Listen as real as I can put it. Sometimes you have to let go of what’s hurting you, even if it hurts you to let go. ⁣Nothing is worth losing your peace. You’ll never heal your heart by staying in the pain that’s destroying your life. ⁣
𝘚𝘵𝘳𝘢𝘪𝘨𝘩𝘵 𝘜𝘱⁣
⁣
⁣#love #family #friendship #relationships #trentshelton #real ⁣
